    <h1>Guerrilla Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">Unconventional, low-cost tactics that promote a brand in unexpected ways — using creativity, surprise, and environment to generate attention and word-of-mouth without large advertising budgets. Named after guerrilla warfare's asymmetric approach to outmanoeuvring larger opponents.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
